name: Mass Healing Word
level: 3
school: evocation
casting_time: bonusaction
range: feet 60
has_v_component
duration: instant
description: "As you call out words of restoration, up to six creatures of your choice that you can see within range regain hit points equal to 1d4 + your spellcasting ability modifier. This spell has no effect on undead or constructs."
upcast_description: "When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the healing increases by 1d4 for each slot level above 3rd."
